scrotty NEWS                                          -*- outline -*-

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.1 (TO BE DETERMINED) [stable]

** Installation changes

  The Make rule 'default' has been renamed to 'all', and the
  Make rule 'all' has been renamed to 'everything'. The Make
  rule 'install-all' has been renamed to 'install-everything'.

** Improvements

  The option --raw has been added. This option makes scrotty
  store the images as a portble anymap format image rather
  than as Portable Network Graphics image. With this change
  ImageMagick becomes optional, but you have to opt-out if
  you do not have it.

  Internationalisation support has been added. For the purpose
  of testing, a complete Swedish translation has been included.

  HTML manual can now be built and installed.

** Translations

  The program and the man page has been translated to Swedish.


* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.2 (2015-(10)Dec-01) [stable]

** Documentation

  A man page was added.


* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.1 (2015-(04)Apr-06) [stable]

  Nothing noteworthy in this release.


* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0 (2014-(10)Oct-28) [stable]

  Initial release.

